sub_title: Student of English Language and Culture
summary: As a student of English Language and Culture my interests lie in linguistics, editing and education. I keep up to date on developments and improvements of the educational system in place in The Netherlands, especially the rapid growth of English. As a former TTO (bilingual education) high school student and native English speaker these topics are not only interesting to me, but have played a big role throughout my life, making me more eager to learn more about them and ultimately focus a career around them.
